OL,3,CVideo shows motorcyclist riding at
OL,4,C160mph as he's jailed for dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FA motorcyclist who rode his bike at up
OL,8,Fto 160mph has been jailed for
OL,9,Fdangerous driving.
OL,11,FLewis Baker was caught driving through
OL,12,FBuckingham and Oxfordshire at
OL,13,Fdangerous speeds for sustained periods
OL,14,Fof time on 9 September 2023. He often
OL,15,Fexceeded 130mph on A roads.
OL,17,FBaker himself stated to the courts
OL,18,Fthat he had driven like a "menace".
OL,26,@zD@[OUzD@bO]
