PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783941695
OL,3,CVideo shows motorcyclist riding at
OL,4,C160mph as he's jailed for dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FSenior Investigator, Philip Hanham of
OL,8,Fthe Serious Collision Investigation
OL,9,FUnit, said: "Baker's riding was
OL,10,Fappalling and is the worst I have seen
OL,11,Fon a motorbike in all my 30 years as a
OL,12,Fpolice officer and investigator."
OL,14,FThe 35 year-old was sentenced at
OL,15,FAylesbury Crown Court to 15 months'
OL,16,Fimprisonment and a driving
OL,17,Fdisqualification of ten years.
OL,26,@qD@MOU
