FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783941695
OL,3,CVideo shows motorcyclist riding at
OL,4,C160mph as he's jailed for dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FBaker pleaded guilty to one count of
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and was found not
OL,9,Fguilty by a jury of one count of
OL,10,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,12,FOn passing sentence, HHJ Cooper stated
OL,13,Fthat they felt the standards of riding
OL,14,Fdisplayed by Baker were "as bad as it
OL,15,Fcould be" and that his sentence had to
OL,16,Freflect the multiple breaches of the
OL,17,Flaw committed that day.
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@IO]
