FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783941695
OL,3,CVideo shows motorcyclist riding at
OL,4,C160mph as he's jailed for dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FIn his closing remarks, HHJ Cooper
OL,8,Fsaid that the place for driving at
OL,9,Fthose very high speeds was a
OL,10,Fracetrack, not the public roads.
OL,12,FSenior Investigator, Philip Hanham of
OL,13,Fthe Serious Collision Investigation
OL,14,FUnit, said "On this day of this
OL,15,Fappalling riding, Baker was filming
OL,16,Fhis dangerous riding with the
OL,17,Fintention of sharing with others. This
OL,18,Fshowed his intent to ride in the
OL,19,Fdangerous manner that he was rightly
OL,20,Fsentenced for."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
